Package org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations.formats.mpo

Class MpoGeneAnnotation

java.lang.Object
org.monarchinitiative.phenol.annotations.formats.mpo.MpoGeneAnnotation
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<TermAnnotation>, Identified, TermAnnotation
public final class MpoGeneAnnotation extends Object implements TermAnnotation
Annotation of a HPO term (via its TermId) with genes.

The label of this TermAnnotation is "ENTREZ:${entrez_id}".

Author:
Manuel Holtgrewe, Sebastian Koehler
